- `C:/GitHub/Berreman/Berreman/OpticalConstructor/OpticalConstructor.Domain/CurvedElements.fs` (new) — curved-element domain: `CurvedSurface`, `SurfaceFigure`, `LocalZone`, `sag`, `sampleZones`, `solveZone`, `attachCurvedElement`, `gradeCoating`

